{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stellations is a manic single-player arcade game about careening through mind maps. Pilot yourself through vibrating circuits where each input is tactile, twitchy, delightful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/extras/Detour_1_.gif?t=1728493873\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete circuits by hitting every node in time. Align to the path to gain momentum and shoot off points with timed button presses. Unique points allow you to create new connections, fly between webs, and boost through intersections. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/extras/tangle.gif?t=1728493873\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Structure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Extend the mental map by completing circuits and retrieving nodes. Each sub-level unlocks new connections in the overworld. You're not alone on the webs. Internalize their structure and manoeuvre through one-way paths, accelerating feedback loops, and rumble strips to escape entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/extras/web.gif?t=1728493873\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sound</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every point and line in Stellations reacts to your input with the shimmer and rumble of a frequency modulation synth. Each level is like an instrument you learn to play through your movement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/extras/editor_1_.gif?t=1728493873\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Level Editor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Draw your thought loops in the level editor and navigate them. Decorate them with different line types, textures, words, and entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728493873","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/page.bg.jpg?t=1728493873","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/2035ce6ae2d95b859af843aad04f59ad7c572487/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728493873","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/2035ce6ae2d95b859af843aad04f59ad7c572487/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728493873","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stellations is a manic single-player arcade game about careening through mind maps. Pilot yourself through vibrating circuits where each input is tactile, twitchy, delightful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/extras/Detour_1_.gif?t=1728493873\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete circuits by hitting every node in time. Align to the path to gain momentum and shoot off points with timed button presses. Unique points allow you to create new connections, fly between webs, and boost through intersections. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648200/extras/tangle.gif?t=1728493873\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Structure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Extend the mental map by completing circuits and retrieving nodes. Each sub-level unlocks new connections in the overworld. You're not alone on the webs. Intern